docs {
  # One-click SAN lookup / scan (via FTTH Mobily Toolkit)

  Prasyarat: toolkit jalan di http://localhost:3456
    npm run dev   # di repo FTTH-Mobily-Toolkit

  ### Edit input di Bruno
  Params memakai nilai literal (bukan `{{orderId}}` / `{{customerSAN}}`)
  supaya bisa diedit di tab Params. Env diganti otomatis dari
  environment Bruno yang aktif saat Send.

  ### 01 - Lookup SAN by Order ID
  ### 02 - Find Orders by SAN (scan)
}
